tasks.name: RENN_main1_1721
tasks.description:
This is based off of RENN_main1.py

How to run:
Invoke 32-bit PyATS instance
Can install one via -
/auto/pyats/bin/pyats install --version 19.0 --32bit
Source 32bit TCL-ATS
source /auto/pysw/ats/env.sh

Backup instance - <461> :: source /auto/iconatest53/users/anbharat/pyats/env.sh

easypy RENN_test_job_1721.py -testbed shmandal_testbed.yaml -mailto shmandal

# Sanity + L2
easypy RENN_test_job_1721.py -testbed shmandal_testbed.yaml -mailto shmandal --testcase "['sanity', '03']"
